definitions.definition: A rush of sexual excitement; now specifically, the climax or peak of sexual pleasure , which occurs during sexual activity and which in males may include ejaculation and in females vaginal contractions .
examples: If you want to get an orgasm , I recommend buying a vibrator.

definitions.definition: A creamy white alcoholic cocktail containing amaretto , Irish cream , and coffee liqueur .
